\cb14 Because an agent configuring Google Cloud, Hugging Face, and local systems needs deep system access, I have engineered a\'a0containerized, LangGraph-powered Agentic OS. It operates securely inside a Docker container equipped with the Google Cloud SDK, Hugging Face CLI, GitHub CLI, and a Python-based autonomous loop.\cb1 \
