\fs40 \cf3 \cb14 How this works:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa80\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\fs28 \cf3 \cb14 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 The LLM Core:\'a0It uses OpenAI's\'a0
\f4\fs24 gpt-4o
\f1\fs28 \'a0(or\'a0
\f4\fs24 claude-3.5-sonnet
\f1\fs28 \'a0if you prefer) wired to a modern tool-calling framework (
\f4\fs24 LangGraph
\f1\fs28 ).\cb1 \
\ls3\ilvl0\cb14 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 The Toolset:\'a0It has direct access to read files, write code/configs, and securely execute terminal commands (
\f4\fs24 gcloud
\f1\fs28 ,\'a0
