\fs40 \cf3 \cb14 How this works:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa80\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\fs28 \cf3 \cb14 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
