\f1\fs28 \'a0if you prefer) wired to a modern tool-calling framework (
\f4\fs24 LangGraph
\f1\fs28 ).\cb1 \
\ls9\ilvl0\cb14 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 The Toolset:\'a0It has direct access to read files, write code/configs, and securely execute terminal commands (
