\f1\fs28 ).\cb1 \
\ls9\ilvl0\cb14 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 The Deployment:\'a0Run the single command block below. It will build your directories, write the autonomous Python code, generate the Dockerfile, and provide an auto-start script.\cb1 \
